iBall Splash 2D Black-Yellow:
The Splash 2D presented by iBall is a remarkable mobile phone which has a 2.4 inch display screen and an alphanumeric keypad. The black and yellow colour combination of this phone makes it look stylish. This phone features dual SIM technology 1.3 megapixel camera with digital zoom and MP3 & FM players. GPRS USB and bluetooth connectivity are some of the other highlights of this phone that offers value for money. Storage memory of this phone can be expanded up to 16 GB using a micro SD card.
